128	  <header class="hero">
129	    <div class="wrap">
130	      <h1>Scrum, in one page</h1>
131	      <p class="subhead">A plain-language overview of Scrum — the roles, the five events, the artifacts, and the Sprint that holds them together. Aligned with the current Scrum Guide.</p>
132	    </div>
133	  </header>
134	
135	  <nav class="anchors" aria-label="Section navigation">
136	    <ul>
137	      <li><a href="#roles">Roles</a></li>
138	      <li><a href="#events">Events</a></li>
139	      <li><a href="#artifacts">Artifacts</a></li>
140	      <li><a href="#sprint">Sprint</a></li>
141	    </ul>
142	  </nav>
